Tried running below code to confirm:

```C++
  uint64_t i = 4;
  while (--i)
  { 
  cout<<i;
  }
  cout<<i;
  
```

```C++
  uint64_t i = 4;
  while (i--)
  { 
  cout<<i;
  }
  cout<<i;
  
```

```C++
  uint64_t i = 4;
  while (i)
  { 
   --i;
  cout<<i;
  }
  cout<<i;
  
```

It is also according to coding style mentioned in docs: https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/doc/developer-notes.md#coding-style-c
